1. *Pričam* sa drugaricom. (I'm talking with my friend.)
2. Ona mi *priča* o svojim problemima. (She is telling me about her problems.)
3. *Pričala* sam sa njim pre pola sata. (I was talking with him half an hour ago.)
4. *Priče* su trajale dugo. (The conversations lasted long.)
5. Ona je *pričala* sama sa sobom. (She was talking to herself.)
6. *Pričali* smo o različitim temama. (We were talking about different topics.)
7. Ona *priča* da treba da se promeni. (She is saying that she needs to change.)
8. *Pričaju*ću ti o tome kada se sretnemo. (I will talk to you about it when we meet.)